headline: 1 Healthcare Stock Worth Your Attention and 2 Facing Headwinds
summary: Personal health and wellness is one of the many secular tailwinds for healthcare companies. Shareholders who bet on the industry have been rewarded lately as healthcare stocks have returned 14.4% over the past six months, topping the S&P 500 by 4 percentage points.
